    <!-- CONVERSATION 1: Conversation 1 -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_precond">
        <text>req_story_npc:esc_2_12_stalker_wolf</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_repeatable">
        <text>0</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_storyline_id">
        <text>loner_wolf_storyline</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_open">
        <text>Stalker, get over here. I need someone who knows which end of the rifle lead comes out of, and you look in shape. </text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_choice_1">
        <text>You look like you haven't slept in days. What's the problem?</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_reply_1">
        <text>It's the Garbage. There's a smuggler baron up there named Kovalchuk. He’s set up a toll on the main route. He's bleeding our rookies dry, confiscating their artifacts, and leaving them to the mutants. I sent one of my best scouts, a kid named Artyom, to trail Kovalchuk to his main stash. We were going to hit him where it hurts.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_outcome_1">
        <text>none</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_cont_1">
        <text>2</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_cont_channel_1">
        <text>f2f</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t2_choice_1">
        <text>Let me guess. Artyom missed his check in.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t2_reply_1">
        <text>Three hours ago. Artyom is a ghost, he doesn't just 'miss' check-ins. His last coordinates were a collapsed tunnel on the eastern edge of the Garbage. I can't leave the village undefended to go looking for him. I need you to go up there, find Artyom, and find out what Kovalchuk is up to.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t2_outcome_1">
        <text>none</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t2_cont_1">
        <text>3</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t2_cont_channel_1">
        <text>f2f</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t3_choice_1">
        <text>I'll find him, Wolf. Hang tight. </text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t3_reply_1">
        <text>Good man</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t3_outcome_1">
        <text>none</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t3_choice_2">
        <text>Sorry, I'm not a charity. Sidorovich pays me for work. What are you offering?</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t3_reply_2">
        <text>I don't have Sidorovich's rubles, but I have a stash of AP rounds and some meds but if you really impress me..I might throw something extra waiting for you if you bring me solid intel. Just get it done.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t3_outcome_2">
        <text>none</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t3_choice_3">
        <text>Kovalchuk? Doesn't he travel with heavily armed guards? At least send me with someone. </text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t3_reply_3">
        <text>Hmm to be truthful, I've been holding back Hip from going there herself, have a chat with her. Don't fuck this up. </text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t3_outcome_3">
        <text>spawn_custom_npc:mia</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t3_cont_3">
        <text>4</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t3_cont_channel_3">
        <text>f2f</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t3_cont_npc_3">
        <text>npc:mia</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t4_open">
        <text>Uhm..yes?</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t4_choice_1">
        <text>oh shit...forgot what i was saying.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t4_reply_1">
        <text>I'm busy.</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_1_t4_outcome_1">
        <text>none</text>
    </string>
